reviews.text:
NEW UPDATE:
This really nice restaurant/bar is now closed!
But Google still hasn’t updated its information. 
So I went there last week and reception of the building said it's closed :(
Please note that guys.

22 Jul 2019

==========

Nice place to hang out and chill with friends. Very nice scenery. Before 8:30 there's happy hour!

Seems like a bit of a secret, certainly during the afternoon. Two Afternoon Tea set options available.  For the views, less so the food, I think it's a good deal at $298 for two people. No one else there when we arrived at 2.30 pm. Happy Hour is also pretty good and runs from 12 pm to 9 pm daily. Oh and they have crazy toothpicks!
Regular Friday happy hour drinks, staff is mostly friendly, prices are only acceptable, but the view is amazing and it's just so convenient!

Came here for post dinner drinks, drinks are on the expensive side, but there is a outdoor area where you can overlook the beautiful Victoria Harbour. The negative side of this outdoor area is that people allow to smoke. I would suggest to come during the early evening, which they will have less people and you can also see a better view

Very nice view. U can enjoy firework in lunar new year. 

For the food, quite expensive. $600 for a set dinner. Generous volume. Delicious. 

Seating not good. Strong air conditioning.
